        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0003",
      "text": "4.2.43.2.4  Locally-Enabled VF_ID List Descriptor",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        327.03,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0004",
      "text": "The format of the Locally-Enabled VF_ID List descriptor is shown in table 128.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        440.97,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0005",
      "text": "VF_ID Bitmap:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.97,
        164.46,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0006",
      "text": " Each Virtual Fabric is identified by a bit in the VF_ID Bitmap. The high-order bit rep-",
      "bbox": [
        164.52,
        250.97,
        540.16,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0007",
      "text": "resents VF_ID zero, each successive bit represents the successive VF_ID, and the low-order bit rep-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.97,
        540.05,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0008",
      "text": "resents VF_ID 4095. Virtual Fabric K is allowed on the Interconnect_Port if the Kth bit of the VF_ID",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.97,
        539.99,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0009",
      "text": "Bitmap is set to one; is disallowed if the Kth bit of the VF_ID Bitmap is set to zero. The bit represent-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.97,
        540.13,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0010",
      "text": "ing the Control VF_ID (see FC-FS-2) shall be set to zero.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.97,
        348.23,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0011",
      "text": "The list of Virtual Fabrics operational over a link is computed by performing a bit-wise ‘AND’ between",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.97,
        539.85,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0012",
      "text": "the received VF_ID Bitmap and the locally configured VF_ID Bitmap.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        399.47,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0013",
      "text": "4.2.43.2.5  Vendor Specific Descriptor",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        274.29,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0014",
      "text": "The format of the Vendor Specific descriptor is shown in table 129.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        382.96,
        390.59,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0015",
      "text": "T10 Vendor ID:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        166.51,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p135_s0016",
      "text": " Shall be set to the Vendor’s T10 Vendor ID.",
      "bbox": [
        166.5,
        574.96,
        362.09,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
